@startuml
title Incident Management Process - Activity Diagram

start

:Monitoring System detects a Failure;
note right: e.g., Matching Engine Timeout

:Trigger Alert to On-Call Engineer;

if (Critical Priority?) then (yes)
  :Notify Senior SRE via PagerDuty;
else (no)
  :Log Incident in Jira/Ticket System;
endif

:Engineer analyzes Logs & Metrics;
:Identify Root Cause;

partition "Resolution Phase" {
  :Apply Fix (Rollback or Patch);
  :Verify System Health;
}

:Close Incident Ticket;

partition "Documentation Phase" {
  :Draft Postmortem Report;
  note right: Required by Project Document (Page 10)
  :Review with Engineering Team;
  :Update Standard Operating Procedures (SOP);
}

stop
@enduml
